  "An oyster farmer on the Pacific coast reports that baby oysters are having difficulty forming shells. Water chemistry tests show the ocean pH has dropped from 8.2 to 8.1 in the region. Why would a seemingly small pH change of 0.1 cause such a significant problem?": "",
